香港人必勝法</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n頭盔：我唔知可唔可行，希望呢個建議對大家有用<br />\n<br />\n佢地日日Chok OT，跟本唔想我地停，我地就係咁比佢打，佢就係咁係我地個袋收錢！<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">一定要諗辦法攪佢地份糧先！凍結佢地薪金！</span></strong></span><br />\n要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">區議員同埋立法會議員請做野！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n停左佢地人工起碼班狗冇心機做野先，佢地一定士氣低落，打人都冇打得咁大力！唔停佢地人工只會，越黎越出力咁打，因為我地越反抗，佢就越多錢，佢地唔會想我地停，仲會搵鬼攪事！<br />\n<br />\n同埋清算黑警好簡單，就算佢地矇哂面、冇Number都好首先抽撚哂有份出OT既警察出黎先，全部都有出糧紀錄，邊D有份出過OT既一定係黑警，再查佢地幾時有OT、邊一更、邊個地點有OT過！"},{"pid":"2d13662a31e63d870f41733c9cc8aa83a83efe00","tid":1765773,"uid":213834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"你點教的"},{"pid":"5bd4186b65f8a15e34b7ee1a9e74991dd3fa6cda","tid":1765773,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bc68e02f66b335e4aeba1ec01eeea2164d4692b","tid":1765773,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"260327dbadb8db3a0bbb3fb57007373c48e88b51","tid":1765773,"uid":312193,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T06:11:07.000Z","msg":"sorry sir<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V01HtMA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV01HtMA.png&h=26dc50c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbV1KjV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbV1KjV.gif&h=925a33a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:26:53.000Z","msg":"呢個好得意，點整架？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"人哋整嘅<br />\n我負責save低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd723f65b7edab61cea726d84a479ca78492052","tid":1765773,"uid":242846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"多謝鳩蛇<br />\nBtw你點影的"},{"pid":"79297d3b73dfe016f06b94e1cd735cbeac5bbbad","tid":1765773,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bd4186b6